							<div id="headdh" class="art-box" style="padding-top: 10px;"><div class="pindex"><ul class="cl"><li> <span class="num">1</span><a href="http://switch.tgbus.com/news/201703/20170327131511.shtml"><font color="red">第 1 页：角色</font></a></li><li> <span class="num">2</span><a href="http://switch.tgbus.com/news/201703/20170327131511_2.shtml">第 2 页：两种战斗类型</a></li><li> <span class="num">3</span><a href="http://switch.tgbus.com/news/201703/20170327131511_3.shtml">第 3 页：与怪物战斗</a></li></ul></div></div>
			
