							<p></p>
<p>　　SQAURE ENIX预定于2017年发售的PS4/3DS平台游戏《勇者斗恶龙11 寻找逝去的时光》官网更新，公开新角色与战斗系统相关最新情报，游戏具体发售日将于4月11日举办的直播节目中公布，此外NS版本也确定会推出。</p>
<p align="center"><a style="FONT-SIZE: medium; FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal" href="http://switch.tgbus.com/UploadFiles/201703/20170327132130525.jpg" target="_blank"><img src="http://img3.tgbusdata.cn/v2/thumb/jpg/M0IwQSw1ODAsMTAwLDQsMywxLC0xLDAscms1MCw2MS4xNTIuMjQyLjE=/u/switch.tgbus.com/UploadFiles/201703/20170327132131550.jpg"></a></p>
<p>　<strong>　角色</strong></p>
<p>　　高贵的女武斗家 马尔缇娜</p>
<p>　　“和你一起保护大家，这就是我的战斗。”</p>
<p align="center"><a style="FONT-SIZE: medium; FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal" href="http://switch.tgbus.com/UploadFiles/201703/20170327132131418.jpg" target="_blank"><img src="http://img3.tgbusdata.cn/v2/thumb/jpg/MUM5NSw1ODAsMTAwLDQsMywxLC0xLDAscms1MCw2MS4xNTIuMjQyLjE=/u/switch.tgbus.com/UploadFiles/201703/20170327132131365.jpg"></a></p>
<p align="center"><a style="FONT-SIZE: medium; FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal" href="http://switch.tgbus.com/UploadFiles/201703/20170327132131624.jpg" target="_blank"><img src="http://img3.tgbusdata.cn/v2/thumb/jpg/QkZCOCw1ODAsMTAwLDQsMywxLC0xLDAscms1MCw2MS4xNTIuMjQyLjE=/u/switch.tgbus.com/UploadFiles/201703/20170327132132364.jpg"></a></p>
<p>　　谜之老人 罗</p>
<p>　　“我一直在等着你的到来。”</p>
